SEC. 6.

The Governing Board.

â The governing body of the University shall be the Board of Regents, hereinafter referred to as the Board, which shall be composed of the following:

(a)

The Chairperson of the Commission on Higher Education (CHED), Chairperson;

(b)

The President of the University, Vice Chairperson;

(c) The Chairperson of the Committee on Education, Arts and Culture of the Senate, Member;

(d)

The Chairperson of the Committee on Higher and Technical Education of the House of Representatives, Member;

(e)

The Regional Director of the National Economic and Development Authority (NED.A) Region V, Member;

(f)

The Regional Director of the Department of Agriculture (DA) Region V, Member;

(g) The Regional Director of the Department of Science and Technology (DOST

